              .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
                .row
                  .col-xs-8.no-padding
                    h1 Brew
                    h4 The Planeswalker's Compendium
                  .col-xs-4.no-padding
                    ul.mj-list
                      li.responsive-text
                        a(href='https://github.com/Spinaldash/mtgapp', target='_blank', title='Visit the Github Repo')
                          i.fa-stack.fa-2x
                            i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
                            i.fa.fa-github-alt.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
                      li.responsive-text
                        a(href='http://brew.michaeljperez.net', target='_blank', title='Visit the Site')
                          i.fa-stack.fa-2x
                            i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
                            i.fa.fa-cogs.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
                  .row
                    .col-xs-12
                      h3 Abstract:
                      p  Brew was conceived as a tool to help players prepare for competitive Magic: The Gathering events. Brew is a web-application that allows the user to visualize M:TG cards in unique and powerful ways. Brew showcases powerful custom filtering with Angular, and dynamically creates and completes an API as it is used.
                    .col-xs-12.hidden-xs
                      h3 What makes it cool:
                      ul
                        li Dynamically creates/configures its api as it is used.
                        li Access to every card in standard play.
                        li Powerful filtering and sorting with Angular.
                    .col-xs-12
                      h3 Tech Featured:
                      .labels
                        .featured
                          span(title='Amazon Web Services').label.label-info.mj-label AWS
                          span(title='AngularJS').label.label-warning.mj-label AngularJS
                          span(title='MongoDB').label.label-info.mj-label MongoDB
                          span(title='Javascript').label.label-info.mj-label Javascript
                          span(title='HTML/CSS').label.label-info.mj-label HTML/CSS
                          span(title='NodeJS').label.label-info.mj-label NodeJS
                          span(title='HapiJS').label.label-info.mj-label HapiJS
              .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
                .row
                  .col-xs-4.col-sm-12
                    a.fancybox-thumb(rel="fancybox-thumb", href="/assets/images/brew/Brew_1.png" )
                      img.mjbox.thumbnail(src="/assets/images/brew/Brew_1.png", alt="Brew1")
