                    .col-xs-12
                      h3 Abstract:
                      p  Toor is the project that won our 4 man team the LAUNCH 2015 hackathon SABRE API award. We wanted to create a better way to plan your next vacation. TOOR utilizes the SABRE API to provide you with destination options and Twitter to help build an itinerary. I worked closely with another Front-End Developer on this project.
                    .col-xs-12.hidden-xs
                      h3 What makes it cool:
                      ul
                        li: a(href='http://challengepost.com/software/toor-4z8zg', target='_blank') Hackathon award winner.
                        li Powered by Sabre and Twitter APIs.
                        li Created in 48 hours by a team of 4.
